%style
  :sass
    table.icon_test
      .iconx
        outline: 1px solid #ccc
      
      .iconx
        background-repeat: no-repeat !important
        background-position: 0 50% !important
       
      .smallx
        padding-left: 20px !important
        &.inlinex
          padding: 1px 0
          
      .largex
        padding-left: 36px !important
        background-image: url(/images/default/32.jpg)
        &.singlex.block, &.singlex.inline-block
          line-height: 32px
          height: 32px
          overflow: hidden
        &.multix.block, &.multix.inline-block
          min-height: 32px
        &.inline
          opacity: 0.5

      .block
        display: block
      .inline
        display: inline
      .inline-block
        display: inline-block
      
      td, th
        padding: 20px
        border: 1px dotted #ccc
      td.good
        background: #dfd
      td.bad
        background: #fdd
      td.ok
        background: #ffd

%table.icon_test
  %tr
    %th   
    %th inline
    %th block
    %th inline-block
  %tr
    %td 1 line, small icon
    %td.good
      .iconx.singlex.smallx.inline.info_16 aa aaaa aaaaa aaaaa
      %br padding 1px
    %td.good
      .iconx.singlex.smallx.block.info_16 bbb b b bbbbbbb bbbbb bb
      no hacks
    %td.good
      .iconx.singlex.smallx.inline-block.info_16 ccccc cc cccc
      %br no hacks
  %tr
    %td 1 line, big icon
    %td.bad
      .iconx.singlex.largex.inline dddddd dddd ddd
      %br nothing works well, avoid.
    %td.ok
      .iconx.singlex.largex.block eeee eeee eeeeeeeee ee
      line-height 32px, height 32px, error: multi line overflow is hidden
    %td.ok
      .iconx.singlex.largex.inline-block fffff ffff ffffffff ffff fff
      %br same as block
  %tr
    %td multi line, small icon
    %td.good
      .iconx.smallx.inline.color_wheel_16 gggg gggg g gg ggg ggggggg gggg gggg ggg gggg ggg ggg g ggggg gg g g 
      %br
      .iconx.smallx.inline.color_wheel_16 gggg gggg g gg
      %br
      padding 1px
    %td.good
      .iconx.smallx.block.color_wheel_16 hhhh hhhh hhhh hh hhhhhhhh hhhhh hhhhh hhhhhhh hhhhh hhhh hhhh hhhhh hh
      .iconx.smallx.block.color_wheel_16 hhhh hhhh hhhh hh
      no hacks
    %td.good
      .iconx.smallx.inline-block.color_wheel_16 iiii iiii ii i i iiiiiiii iiiii ii i iiiii ii iiiii iiii iiiiiii
      %br
      .iconx.smallx.inline-block.color_wheel_16 iiii iiii ii
      %br
      no hacks
  %tr
    %td multi line, big icon
    %td.bad
      .iconx.largex.multix.inline jjjjjj jjjjj jjjjjj jjjj jjjjj jjj j j jjjjjjjj jjjjj jjjjj jjj j jjj j jj jjj
      %br nothing works well, avoid.
    %td.ok
      .iconx.largex.multix.block kkkk kkkkkkkkkkk kkkkkkk kkkkkkkk k kk k kkkkk kk k kkkkkk kkkkkk kkkkk kkkk
      .iconx.largex.multix.block kkkk kkkkkkkkkkk
      min-height 32px, error: text not centered if only one line of text.
    %td.ok
      .iconx.largex.multix.inline-block llll lllllllll lllll llllll lll llll lllll l llll l l llllllllll l ll llll
      %br
      .iconx.largex.multix.inline-block llll lllllllll
      %br same as block

.p notes

.p small icon, inline: setting a 1px padding seems to change the rendering algorithm in such a way that the icon is more vertically centered on the text.

.p big icon, 1 line: together, setting line-height and height will center the text on the icon, give the icon enough space, and ensure that we don't break across multiple lines (multiple lines look bad when line-height is set).

.p big icon, multi-line: min-height allows the icon to be visible, but does not center the icon vertically if there is only one line of text.
